<font size = 6>Porcupines - Deagle5Drop</font>
<font size = 2>
My first map designed for my clan server, but feel free to download and use it yourself.

Spawn points are next to each other at the top whilst the action takes place below in a drop down to the classic Deagle 5 Layout.

High Dynamic Range provides all the lighting and highlights you'd want on high spec pc's but the map has been designed to look good on those with not such cash to spend on the monsters they dream of building! Optimized just to make sure those people don't suffer in their FPS's for good looks, (personally I think it looks great without or with HDR).

Enjoy the Map.

[CK] Porcupine
